-- models/intermediate/int_deduped_returns.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        return_id,
        item_id,
        return_date,
        reason,
        status,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (
            PARTITION BY item_id
            ORDER BY return_id ASC
        ) AS row_num
    FROM {{ ref('stg_returns') }}
)
SELECT
    return_id,
    item_id,
    return_date,
    reason,
    status
FROM source
WHERE row_num = 1
```

```sql
-- models/intermediate/int_products_with_category.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        p.product_id,
        p.name,
        p.category_id,
        c.name AS category_name
    FROM {{ ref('stg_products') }} p
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('stg_categories') }} c
        ON c.category_id = p.category_id
)
SELECT
    product_id,
    name,
    category_id,
    category_name
FROM source
```

```sql
-- models/mart/fct_product_returns_by_category.sql
WITH source AS (
    SELECT
        COALESCE(pc.category_name, '(unknown)') AS category_name,
        oi.item_id,
        r.return_id
    FROM {{ ref('stg_order_items') }} oi
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_products_with_category') }} pc
        ON pc.product_id = oi.product_id
    LEFT JOIN {{ ref('int_deduped_returns') }} r
        ON r.item_id = oi.item_id
)
SELECT
    category_name,
    COUNT(item_id) AS total_items_sold,
    COUNT(return_id) AS total_items_returned,
    CAST(COUNT(return_id) AS DECIMAL(10,2)) / NULLIF(COUNT(item_id), 0) * 100 AS return_rate
FROM source
GROUP BY
    category_name
